  lines:
  - Nicely done again with the history lesson. There's loads more to be taught so
    let's kick it up a notch.
  - This time we will be ensuring the robots know about structured, semi-structured
    and unstructured data.
  - You know where the terminal is! Best of luck. Speak to my colleague beside it
    if you need extra assistance.
